profile:
TSR PEST CONTROL & WILDLIFE REMOVAL offers you true, safe, and reliable pest and wildlife control services across the Greater Toronto and Hamilton Areas. TSR is a fully licensed and insured, Canadian-owned company that guarantees the state of the art pest control and wildlife removal solutions. Our staff have over thirty years' experience in the pest control industry and can quickly detect and solve your pest problem. We will be glad to assess the pest and wildlife situation in your home or business on short notice and identify the most effective pest control action plan. 

AT TSR, our approach to pest control is based on three pillars: 
1) Child- and pet-aware
2) environmentally conscious
3) remaining pest-free in the long-term. An essential part of our pest control programs focuses on eliminating the source of the pest, in addition to treating the existing pest population within the structure. TSR has access to the right tools and expertise to help you achieve a pest-free environment and remain pest-free in the long run. 

Please make sure to check our video and photo galleries on our HomeStars profile, our website[ www.tsrpestcontrol.ca ], and our YouTube channel [ https://www.youtube.com/c/tsrpestcontrol ] to gain a better understanding of how we work.

services:
Welcome To Eco Pest Control
Trusted & Reliable Pest Control Company In The GTA
Homes get infested with termites, rodents, pests and other harmful insects without the homeowners realizing it. Pests and rodents can carry harmful diseases that can impact the safety of your home and business. If you’re looking for a pest control solution, then Eco Pest Control is the place to get the right assistance. We aren’t your typical exterminators; we are full-service pest control experts in the GTA region who help you deal with getting rid of unwanted pests and ensuring that they don’t return. No matter what species you’re dealing with, our environment-friendly products will help remove them all.

Bed Bug Control

Don’t let the bedbug suck your blood anymore. Kill them before they contaminate your blood and your life.


Rodent Control
Rodents are dangerous for both your health and home. Let us help you get rid of these rodents so they don’t infect your home and disturb your peace.


Ant Control
Get the permanent remedy for ant control. Take our services and get rid of these unwanted attackers forever.


Spider Control
Remove unwanted/unpleasant spiders for a long term with our latest spider control solutions.


Cockroach Control
Afraid of Cockroaches? Eliminate them today from your property. Don’t give them a comfortable environment for growth and development.


Bee & Wasp Removal
Bees can be life-taking. They are extremely dangerous for human health. Stop their breeding in and around your premises.
